enior GamesSilverArts kickoff on Friday Jan.";i:15;s:97:"18 at Hanes Hosiery Recreation Center but the biggest draw was the new sport of chair volleyball.";i:16;s:187:"Teams from the Salvation Army Senior Center Arbor Acres Retirement Community and Sims Recreation Center demonstrated the difficulty and fun of playing volleyball in a chair using a beach.";i:17;s:53:"This chair volleyball game started about 2 years ago.";i:18;s:132:"Executive Director Lynda Greene said People who are not seniors assume that all seniors want to do is to knit crochet and eat jello.";i:19;s:84:"That is so far from the truth The video shares that 28 of people ages 65 live alone.";i:20;s:43:"This can lead to isolation and poor health.";i:21;s:88:"It may seem like a simple game but chair volleyball is scoring big points among seniors.";i:22;s:67:"Not only does it provide vital exercise it battles another problem.";i:23;s:53:"Chair Volleyball Rules - Hamilton County Health Dept.";i:24;s:108:"Chair volleyball definitely was a lot of fun for those who came out for it for the first time the other day.";i:25;s:43:"Wednesdays at 1030 AM at the senior center.";i:26;s:53:"Chair Volleyball Rules - Hamilton County Health Dept.";i:27;s:28:"2 Table of Contents Section.";i:28;s:71:"Chair Volleyball Bylaws 3 Code of Conduct 5 Overview 6 Rules of Play 7.";i:29;s:141:"California Senior Games Chair Volleyball Rules Chair Volleyball Chair volleyball is a physical activity that provides a fun way to be active.";i:30;s:176:"Because players are required to remain seated chair volleyball allows those with physical limitations to participate on a level playing field with those who may be more active.";i:31;s:92:"Indoor chair volleyball is a new activity taking senior centers across the country by storm.";i:32;s:83:"It is played with two teams of at least six players with a shorter 5-foot-high net.";i:33;s:40:"The volleyball is actually a beach ball.";i:34;s:83:"Rules are similar to regular volleyball except for the one cheek on the chair rule.";i:35;s:73:"The Seniors Chair Volleyball Tournament is open to 55 Co-Ed Senior Teams.";i:36;s:91:"Registration is limited to the first twenty-six 26 teams with eight 8 people to the roster.";i:37;s:93:"Please complete the Registration Form for each team and the Liability Waiver for each player.";i:38;s:69:"The deadline to submit a roster will be August 31 2020 NO EXCEPTIONS.";i:39;s:57:"Senior Chair Volleyball is a growing sport among Seniors.";i:40;s:161:"This game is played similar to volleyball with the difference being that it played with a 20-inch beach ball and players are seated at all times during the game.";i:41;s:173:"The benefits of playing will improve their cardiovascular fitness increase joint flexibility enhances and maintains muscle tone and endurance and it provides an opportunity.";i:42;s:41:"Balloon Volleyball in a Chair of players.";i:43;s:119:"2 - The way this specific game was variated it is made for senior citizens but it could always be altered for all ages.";i:44;s:150:"- 1 sturdy large colored balloon have extra just in case balloon pops - 1 Volleyball net - 10 flyswatters depending on how many participants you have.";i:45;s:104:"Parkway Place a faith-based senior living community is doing that for its residents with a unique sport.";i:46;s:54:"The game is popular with residents like Aaron Mendoza.";i:47;s:75:"The 92-year-old has played for several years and says its very competitive.";i:48;s:74:"They play every other Wednesday for about an hour and Mendoza says its an.";i:49;s:75:"Basically its volleyball played with a beach ball by people who are seated.";i:50;s:58:"Its something almost anyone can do even from a wheelchair.";i:51;s:48:"So far its attracted mostly people over 60 said.";i:52;s:86:"Chair volleyball is a growing sport among seniors clubs are popping up in many cities.";i:53;s:165:"The game is played similar to volleyball with the difference being that the game is played with a 20-inch beach ball and players are seated at all times during play.";i:54;s:77:"This month the Senior Center is offering a fun new activity Chair Volleyball.";i:55;s:105:"The game is played indoors using a badminton net a beach ball and six chairs on each side facing the net.";i:56;s:52:"Senior Chair Volleyball Tournament in Winston-Salem.";i:57;s:97:"46 seniors ages 50 and older enjoyed playing chair volleyball this morning at the Salvation Army.";i:58;s:132:"46 seniors ages 50 or better competed in a chair volleyball tournament at the Salvation Army on New Walkertown Road Tuesday morning.";i:59;s:55:"Senior Chair Volleyball Tournament in Winston-Salem 16.";i:60;s:138:"The NSGA is a non-profit organization dedicated to motivating active adults to lead a healthy lifestyle through the senior games movement.";i:61;s:21:"T 727 475-1187 Email.";}}